## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="b5cd7-104">方法必须是静态和公共的。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b5cd7-104">The method must be static and public.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b5cd7-105">它必须返回 WMI 类的所有实例的集合。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b5cd7-105">It must return a collection of all instances of the WMI class.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b5cd7-106">集合可以是任何可转换为 <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable>类型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b5cd7-106">The collection can be of any type convertible to <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable>.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="b5cd7-107">下面的示例演示如何使用枚举器特性标记用于枚举类的实例的方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b5cd7-107">The following example shows how to use the Enumerator attribute to mark a method that is used to enumerate instances of a class.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b5cd7-108">在这种情况下，枚举方法使用 <xref:System.Diagnostics.Process> 类来检索在计算机上运行的所有进程。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b5cd7-108">In this case, the Enumerate method uses the <xref:System.Diagnostics.Process> class to retrieve all of the processes running on the computer.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
[ManagementEnumerator]  
public static IEnumerable Enumerate()  
{  
   Process[] rgProcesses = Process.GetProcesses();  
   for (int i = 0; i < rgProcesses.Length; i++)  
   {  
      yield return new ProcessProvider(rgProcesses[i]);  
   }  
}  
```
